考虑。（央广网）减免证券交易印花税呼声渐高 分析人士认为当前具备调整必要性和空间"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-dd023c360035a6d6be277c9b1ed5d1a2_720w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "43 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/617720111"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I9L7Jztz5pKYMEAMaCDk5NTUxMzYxIIr59aYGMAA4PkAUcgk2MTc3MjAxMTF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "21_1692280953.506500", "card_id": "Q_614467626", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 63}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "猫砂盆总有隐隐的臭味传来，哪种猫砂可以做到一猫拉屎「全屋不臭」？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-d02d9562b83eed65516728eb97456bac_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "43 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/614467626"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I9L7Jztz5pKYMEAMaCDk4ODI4NTY2IJ6ojqYGMAA4RkAVcgk2MTQ0Njc2MjZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "22_1692280953.506916", "card_id": "Q_617042409", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 55}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "武直会不会被边缘化？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "注意是在步行载具量产的情况下。武直可以干的步行载具也可以干，而且要节能得多"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-bec2669142d003a970472c0fe12f5bc6_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "43 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/617042409"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I9L7Jztz5pKYMEAMaCDk5NDAwNjQzILH63qYGMAA4eEAWcgk2MTcwNDI0MDl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "23_1692280953.50