d_specific": {"answer_count": 106}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "媒体称「以暂停新股发行来救市不可取」，如何看待此事？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "文章称，随意按下 IPO「暂停键」对市场的伤害是显而易见的。一些优质企业的上市步伐被迫中止，融资难、过度依赖间接融资等难题无法得到缓解，资本市场资源配置效率将受到影响，服务实体经济功能因此弱化。同时，随着市场入口的「扎紧」，上市公司资源稀缺性加剧，炒作壳资源的风气或将随之抬头等。在全面注册制下，新股发行定价实行市场化，资本市场改革已迈出决定性的一步。「暂停 IPO 以救市」，无疑与市场化改革方向相悖，既无助于投资者形成稳定预期，对资本市场运行秩序也将造成严重扰乱。IPO 不是影响市场走势的决定性因素，也不应成为投资者投资决策的首要依据。市场各方应坚定市场化改革方向不动摇，坚持价值投资不放弃，共同呵护资本市场稳中有进、行稳致远。 （来源：）"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-8b6e395190e3cfaf127d7bc858ecfbc1_720w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "42 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/617709198"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I9L7Jztz5pKYMEAMaCDk5NTQ4OTQxIKq29aYGMAA4hgFAGnIJNjE3NzA5MTk4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "27_1692280953.509093", "card_id": "Q_614044123", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 32}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "什么样的珠宝首饰更受人喜欢？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-1fa8e020e8ef54be50b0c8930d82802f_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "42 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/614044123"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I9L7Jztz5pKYMEAMaCDk4NzM0NTQ1IJ+3gqYGMAA4RkAbcgk2MTQwNDQxMjN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "28_1692280953.509420", "card_id": "Q_614474880", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 27}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "你买过哪些「离谱但确实好用」的养宠好物？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-07752b69fa909c5e66ebf1d5e2252fba_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "42 万热度", "font_color": "", "backg